videos.description: Josh Jackson gets the steal and throws the long pass to Landon Lucas for the first basket for Kansas.
videos.headline: Jackson's  steal leads to  Lucas dunk to opening the scoring for Kansas

videos.description: Kansas State's Xavier Sneed gets the steal and Wesley Iwundu tips in the missed layup.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Sneed gets the steal that leads to a tip shot in win

videos.description: Kansas's Carlton Bragg  passes it  to Legerald Vick and he dunks over Kansas State's DJ Johnson.
videos.headline: Kansas with the great ball movement ends with Vick dunking over defender

videos.description: Kansas head coach  Bill Self happy with his teams effort in 1st half and the way they are competing.
videos.headline: Kansas head coach  Bill Self happy with his teams effort in 1st half

videos.description: Devonte Graham finds Landon Lucas down low and Lucas slams it down over D.J. Johnson plus the foul.
videos.headline: Kansas' Graham finds Lucas for the dunk over the defender and-1

videos.description: Kansas State's Xavier Sneed misses the 3 pointer but Wesley Iwundu puts back missed shot.
videos.headline: Kansas State gets the offensive rebound and the put back

videos.description: Josh Jackson is on the break and is blocked by Kansas State's Dean Wade.
videos.headline: Kansas State's Wade doesnt give up and destroys Jackson's layup

videos.description: Kansas guard Frank Mason breaks down his team's 74-71 win on the road against rival Kansas State.
videos.headline: Mason: 'It just took a great effort to come here and get a win'

videos.description: Breaking down Frank Mason performance in the 74-71 victory for Kansas over Kansas State
videos.headline: Breaking down Frank Mason performance in the win

videos.description: Josh Jackson and Frank Mason III combine to score 39 points in No. 3 Kansas' 74-71 victory over Kansas State.
videos.headline: Kansas holds off Kansas State
